    public abstract class ChatIntentProvider<T extends ChatPlatform>
extends RuntimeIntentProvider<T>
    An abstract chat RuntimeIntentProvider.

    This class is extended by provider of platforms extending the ChatPlatform, and ensures that all the chat-related context variables have been set before triggering actions associated to the computed event.

    • Method Detail

      • sendEventInstance

        public void sendEventInstance(EventInstance eventInstance,
                              JarvisSession session)
        Sends the provided eventInstance and session for computation to the Jarvis core component.

        This method can be extended to perform specific checks before triggering actions (e.g. ensure that a specific context variable has been set).

        This method checks that the context variables defined in ChatUtils have been initialized by the concrete provider. This ensures that all the providers extending ChatIntentProvider set the same set of variables and can be used transparently in execution models.

        Overrides:
        sendEventInstance in class RuntimeEventProvider<T extends ChatPlatform>
        Parameters:
        eventInstance - the EventInstance to send to the Jarvis core component
        session - the JarvisSession associated to the provided eventInstance
